game.name: Halloween Special Party Cake
game.description:
Wow! Halloween has just approached and you have lots of preparations to do. Some of your friends want to eat the delicious cake made by your expert hands. Would you like to prepare it for your best friends? Join Halloween Special Party Cake and be prepared to cook a wonderful special cake to celebrate this Halloween in the right spirit! Make sure to follow the instructions properly to achieve your goal. Common girls! You have the guts to get the job done timely.

We are pretty sure that your ultimate cooking abilities can guide you towards a successful result. Decorate it with all the useful and attractive items and let the world show that you are best in preparing a delicious cake in this brand new girls game! Both of your princesses Anna and Elsa rely on your cooking abilities a lot so do not disappoint them. Start by selecting the stand on which you put your cake! Then decide a nice plate along with the matching three layers of the cake in this HTML5 cooking challenge.

Feel free to make different types of combos like green, purple and orange! You can also add colors like blue, yellow or pink. There are multiple decoration items like scorpion tails, spider webs or bats, spiders and pumpkins to choose from.  The drawings of witches, black cats or ghosts can make your can cake decoration fabulous. Two skulls with roses or a haunted house will work as a wonderful centerpiece. Try out more free cooking games that you can play online without download!
